description:
Jimmy Heath - The Bad and the Beautiful
Producing a documentary film, there's always footage that can't be used in the final film, but stands on its own as revealing. Here is one such clip, which won't be included in "Passing the Torch," my new film about Jazz mentors and their importance. On a break while recording with some amazingly talented high school musicians in Tucson, Arizona, Jimmy Heath remembers another song written by David Raksin, composer of Laura. To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
